{"tid":940530,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人去過新加坡intern","createTime":"2018-12-14T04:08:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-15T04:32:09.000Z","uid":215301,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"7b60b30c47ca56d6f4b2bbcd70168137d0a17ff2","tid":940530,"uid":215301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T04:08:00.000Z","msg":"見到連登有人出過類似post<br />\n但多數係跟學校去<br />\n我想知有冇人係自己一手包辦哂<br />\n由上Singapore intern網apply<br />\n到拎左offer 再申請working pass（student)<br />\n同租埋hostel <br />\n可唔可以分享下<br />\n我見月租都佔左income 一半<br />\n諗緊出唔出去見識下<br />\n<br />\n麻煩大家了"},{"pid":"0b43842cd75355ae8bdeb4f40c6d883d6da01807","tid":940530,"uid":177615,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T04:56:28.000Z","msg":"新加坡同香港好似<br />\n冇咩好見識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申 係sg做過野"},{"pid":"f2406021afbde523329133b17ac1d283e7a83eea","tid":940530,"uid":75692,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"0b43842cd75355ae8bdeb4f40c6d883d6da01807","tid":940530,"uid":177615,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T04:56:28.000Z","msg":"新加坡同香港好似<br />\n冇咩好見識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申 係sg做過野"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T05:29:59.000Z","msg":"熱好撚多"},{"pid":"5839f2f5b2ffb9cd8d44eb4edf5bcd0aa5ad1e1e","tid":940530,"uid":75692,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T05:30:11.000Z","msg":"而且悶過香港好多"},{"pid":"7910267f692d6498ec3fd983616edf2894f9bba9","tid":940530,"uid":23225,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T06:13:50.000Z","msg":"經學校apply intern<br />\n除左公司學校聯絡 其他都自己搞<br />\nSG我覺得都幾好玩 都好掛住果陣果邊住既生活<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fed8aca2f228fdff4ccb027311ba24d3e084519e","tid":940530,"uid":23225,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T06:15:28.000Z","msg":"同埋SG如果大公司應該見識幾廣 始於亞洲總部果邊都好多<br />\n但生活點都似香港無真係英美澳咁"},{"p